001package edu.cnm.deepdive.leavemealone.model.entity;
002
003import androidx.annotation.NonNull;
004import androidx.room.ColumnInfo;
005import androidx.room.Entity;
006import androidx.room.PrimaryKey;
007import java.net.URI;
008import java.time.Instant;
009import java.util.LinkedList;
010import java.util.List;
011
012@Entity(
013    tableName = "alert",
014    indices = {}
015)
016public class Alert {
017
018  @PrimaryKey(autoGenerate = true)
019  @ColumnInfo(name = "alert_id")
020  private long id;
021
022  @ColumnInfo(name = "triggered", index = true)
023  private boolean triggered;
024
025  @ColumnInfo(name = "timestamp", index = true)
026  @NonNull
027  private Instant timestamp = Instant.now();
028
029  private String photoname;
030
031  public long getId() {
032    return id;
033  }
034
035  public void setId(long id) {
036    this.id = id;
037  }
038
039  public boolean isTriggered() {
040    return triggered;
041  }
042
043  public void setTriggered(boolean triggered) {
044    this.triggered = triggered;
045  }
046
047  @NonNull
048  public Instant getTimestamp() {
049    return timestamp;
050  }
051
052  public void setTimestamp(@NonNull Instant timestamp) {
053    this.timestamp = timestamp;
054  }
055
056  public String getPhotoname() {
057    return photoname;
058  }
059
060  public void setPhotoname(String photoname) {
061    this.photoname = photoname;
062  }
063}
